data.description: Seller is offering a concession of $10,000. Very spacious home with large rooms and walk in closets. This home is a perfect work from home alternative with an office, and a sizable laundry/mud room.  Large kitchen with an island, breakfast bar, and plenty of cabinet space.  Upstairs game room. Relax on the balcony/deck while gazing at mother nature as a greenbelt lies directly behind your new home.  Refrigerator and Game room projector and projection screen to convey.
